This library aims to be a port of LessPHP for the popular Minify Library.
It is not a fork of Minify itself as the original project is currently using SVN
on Google Code.

Original LessPHP project: http://leafo.net/lessphp/
Original Minify project: http://code.google.com/p/minify/

My personal website where I'll track down tutorials and major changes:
 http://marco-pivetta.com/